data.description: Welcome to this functional 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom open-concept home in the desirable Westgate community! Located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac street on a nice-sized lot, enjoy the privacy of having neighbors on only one side of your home.  Zoned to highly-acclaimed Cy-Fair ISD schools, with easy access to HWY 290, I-10 and the Grand Parkway with restaurants, shopping and the movie theater just minutes away.  Schedule your tour today!
